eing-set-to-launch-astronauts-to-international-space-station-in-historic-mission%2Famp_articleshow%2F109852522.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22People%20Of%20Pakistan-Occupied%20Kashmir%20Will%20Want%20To%20Join%20India%3A%20Rajnath%20Singh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20never%20give%20up%20its%20claim%20on%20Pakistan-Occupied-Kashmir%20(PoK)%20but%20it%20won't%20have%20to%20capture%20it%20with%20force%20because%20its%20people%2C%20on%20their%20own%2C%20would%20want%20to%20be%20part%20of%20India%20after%20seeing%20the%20development%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20PTI%2C%20Singh%20asserted%20that%20the%20ground%20situation%20has%20improved%20significantly%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20that%20a%20time%20will%20come%20when%20AFSPA%20(Armed%20Forces%20Special%20Powers%20Act)%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20required%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defence%20minister%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20matter%20is%20under%20the%20domain%20of%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20and%20it%20will%20take%20appropriate%20decisions.%20He%20said%20elections%20will%20also%20be%20held%20there%20definitely%2C%20but%20wouldn't%20give%20a%20timeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20India%20will%20not%20have%20to%20do%20anything.%20The%20way%20the%20ground%20situation%20has%20changed%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20way%20the%20region%20is%20witnessing%20economic%20progress%20and%20the%20way%20peace%20has%20returned%20there%2C%20I%20think%20demands%20will%20emerge%20from%20people%20of%20PoK%20that%20they%20should%20merge%20with%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20not%20have%20to%20use%20force%20to%20take%20PoK%20as%20people%20would%20say%20that%20we%20must%20be%20merged%20with%20India.%20Such%20demands%20are%20now%20coming%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20defence%20minister%20asserted%20that%20%26quot%3BPoK%20was%2C%20is%2C%20and%20will%20remain%20ours%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20improvement%20in%20the%20ground%20situation%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Singh%20said%20assembly%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20there%20soon%2C%20but%20did%20not%20give%20a%20timeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20the%20situation%20is%20improving%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20I%20think%20a%20time%20will%20come%20when%20AFSPA%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20required%20there.%20It%20is%20my%20view%20and%20it%20is%20for%20the%20Home%20Ministry%20to%20decide%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AFSPA%20empowers%20security%20forces%20to%20conduct%20operations%20and%20arrest%20anyone%20without%20any%20prior%20warrant.%20It%20also%20gives%20immunity%20to%20the%20forces%20if%20they%20shoot%20someone%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defence%20minister%2C%20referring%20to%20Pakistan's%20proxy%20war%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20said%20Islamabad%20must%20stop%20cross%20border%20terrorism.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20trying%20to%20destabilise%20India%20and%20we%20will%20not%20allow%20it%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20came%20under%20severe%20strain%20after%20India's%20warplanes%20pounded%20a%20Jaish-e-Mohammed%20terrorist%20training%20camp%20in%20Balakot%20in%20Pakistan%20in%20February%202019%20in%20response%20to%20the%20Pulwama%20terror%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20relations%20further%20deteriorated%20after%20India%20on%20August%205%2C%202019%20announced%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20special%20powers%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20the%20bifurcation%20of%20the%20state%20into%20two%20union%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20maintaining%20that%20it%20desires%20normal%20neighbourly%20relations%20with%20Pakistan%20while%20insisting%20that%20the%20onus%20is%20on%20Islamabad%20to%20create%20an%20environment%20free%20of%20terror%20and%20ho