20plans%20like%20rolling%20out%20of%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%20and%20implementing%20the%20'One%20Nation%20One%20Election'%20push%20if%20it%20retains%20power%20for%20the%20third%20consecutive%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defence%20minister%20also%20said%20that%20he%20was%20confident%20that%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20will%20cross%20400%20seats%20and%20the%20BJP%20will%20get%20over%20370%20as%20these%20projections%20were%20made%20after%20detailed%20assessment%20of%20the%20ground%20situation%20and%20not%20made%20only%20for%20public%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20overall%20political%20landscape%2C%20the%20defence%20minister%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20attempting%20to%20disturb%20social%20harmony%20and%20trying%20to%20create%20tensions%20on%20religious%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20attempting%20to%20create%20Hindu-Muslim%20divide%20for%20electoral%20gains.%20The%20Congress%20is%20trying%20to%20create%20tensions%20on%20religious%20lines%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20wants%20to%20disturb%20social%20harmony.%20They%20look%20at%20the%20Muslim%20community%20only%20as%20a%20vote%20bank.%20I%20have%20a%20suggestion%20for%20them%20--%20politics%20should%20not%20be%20done%20only%20for%20forming%20governments.%20The%20aim%20of%20politics%20should%20be%20for%20nation%20building%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20has%20no%20fire%20but%20Congress%20is%20playing%20with%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20said%20people%20of%20the%20country%20will%20repose%20their%20faith%20in%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP's%20tally%20will%20improve%20significantly%20based%20on%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20government%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20seats%20will%20increase%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20West%20Bengal%20and%20we%20will%20get%20some%20seats%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20Our%20account%20will%20open%20in%20Kerala%20as%20well.%20We%20are%20winning%20a%20good%20number%20of%20seats%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20increase%20our%20tally%20in%20Odisha%2C%20Jharkhand%20and%20Assam.%20We%20are%20sweeping%20Chhattisgarh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20asserting%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20cross%20the%20370-mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20the%20BJP's%20seats%20in%20Maharashtra%20will%20come%20down%2C%20he%20did%20not%20give%20a%20direct%20reply%20but%20said%20there%20may%20be%20some%20adjustments%20here%20and%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%20also%20came%20down%20hard%20on%20the%20Congress%20for%20its%20plan%20to%20%26quot%3Bredistribute%26quot%3B%20wealth%2C%20saying%20it%20will%20have%20disastrous%20consequences%20for%20the%20country's%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20concept%20of%20redistribution%20of%20wealth%20will%20trigger%20recession.%20Argentina%20and%20Venezuela%20implemented%20it%20and%20faced%20disastrous%20consequences.%20The%20investors%20will%20lose%20confidence%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20BJP's%20big-ticket%20plans%20like%20implementation%20of%20the%20UCC%20and%20'One%20Nation%20One%20Poll'%20push%20in%20if%20it%20retains%20power%2C%20Singh%20said%20it%20fulfils%20promises%20that%20it%20makes%20to%20the%20people%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20manifesto%2C%20the%20BJP%20pledged%20to%20implement%20the%20UCC%20if%20it%20returns%20to%20power%20after%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20mentioned%20that%20the%20party%20will%20move%20forward%20with%20a%20resolve%20to%20realise%20the%20idea%20of%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20always%20fulfil%20our%20commitments.%20We%20will%20never%20allow%20any%20question%20mark%20on%20our%20credibility%20and%20will%20not%20compromise%20on%20the%20country's%20unity%20and%20integrity.%20We%20implement%20whatever%20we%20say%20in%20our%20manifesto.%20We%20have%20to%20do%20whatever%20we%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20go%20for%20'One%20Nation%20One%20Election.%20We%20will%20take%20views%20of%20every%20quarter%2C%20including%20all%20political%20parties%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20UCC%2C%20the%20defence%20minister%20said%20even%20the%20Constitution-makers%20felt%20a%20need%20for%20it%2C%20as%20it%20is%20mentioned%20in%20the%20directive%20principles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20wants%20to%20create%20fear%20psychosis%3B%20they%20want%20to%20use%20the%20Hindu-Muslim%20card%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20do%20not%20have%20any%20issue.%20They%20want%20to%20form%20a%20government%20by%20dividing%20the%20society%20in%20the%20name%20of%20caste%2C%20creed%20and%20religion%20and%20they%20have%20always%20done%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714885320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F5sm73h2g_rajnath-singh_625x300_11_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-attempting-to-create-hindu-muslim-divide-rajnath-singh-5591857%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20no%20fire%20while%20his%20party%20is%20playing%20with%20fire%20by%20attempting%20to%20create%20Hindu-Muslim%20divide%20for%20electoral%20dividends%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-attempting-to-create-hindu-muslim-divide-rajnath-singh-5591857%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-attempting-to-create-hindu-muslim-divide-rajn