ators%20in%20the%20line%20of%20fire.%20Gavaskar%2C%20however%2C%20didn't%20just%20criticise%20Virat%20but%20also%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20broadcaster%20Star%20Sports%20for%20playing%20that%20rant%20from%20the%20opening%20batter%20'a%20dozen%20times'%20on%20television.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20particular%20post-game%20interview%20has%20been%20shown%20on%20this%20channel%20earlier%20as%20well%2C%20right%20now%2C%20on%20this%20particular%20program%20it%20has%20probably%20been%20shown%20half%20a%20dozen%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20hope%20that%20Star%20Sports%20recognises%20that%20when%20that%20is%20being%20shown%2C%20asking%20where%20are%20the%20critics%2C%20the%20critics%20are%20the%20commentators.%20Your%20Star%20Sports%20commentators%20are%20the%20ones%20from%20whom%20the%20questions%20are%20being%20asked.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20118%2C%20you%20come%20and%20face%20the%20first%20ball%2C%20and%20then%20you%20get%20out%20in%20the%2014th%20or%2015th%20over%20and%20your%20strike%20rate%20is%20118%20-%20if%20you%20want%20applause%20for%20that%2C%20then%20that's%20a%20little%20bit%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20for%20Star%20Sports%20to%20show%20the%20person%20belittling%20their%20own%20commentators%2C%20I'm%20not%20sure%20that's%20a%20great%20thing.%20So%20I%20think%20Star%20Sports%20needs%20to%20understand%20that%20they%20have%20shown%20it%20enough%20times%2C%20everyone's%20got%20the%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESo%20according%20to%20Gavaskar%20saab%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20much%20people%20cry%20on%20kohli%20everyday%20Kohli%20shouldn't%20reply%20his%20critics%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F9yiAYtXrg8%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F9yiAYtXrg8%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20POTT%20(%40KlolZone)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKlolZone%2Fstatus%2F1786760699634729056%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%204%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20all%20played%20a%20bit%20of%20cricket%2C%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20cricket%2C%20but%20we%20speak%20about%20what%20we%20see.%20We%20don't%20necessarily%20have%20any%20likes%20and%20dislikes.%20Even%20if%20we%20have%20likes%20or%20dislikes%2C%20we%20actually%20speak%20on%20what's%20happening.%20So%2C%20I%20would%20be%20very%20disappointed%20if%20Star%20Sports%20show%20this%20once%20more%20because%20that%20will%20be%20questioning%20all%20us%20commentators.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20Said%20On%20Virat%20Kohli's%20Rant%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGavaskar%20was%20one%20of%20those%20pundits%20who%20had%20questioned%20Virat%20Kohli's%20intent%2C%20going%20about%20a%20strike-rate%20of%20around%20120%20as%20his%20team%20suffered%20consecutive%20defeats.%20The%20legendary%20cricketer%20doubled%20down%20on%20the%20RCB%20star%2C%20asking%20if%20he%20needed%20appreciation%20for%20a%20strike-rate%20of%20118.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCommentators%20questioned%20only%20when%20his%20strike-rate%20was%20118%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20said%2C%20responding%20to%20Kohli's%20rant.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20too%20sure.%20I%20don't%20watch%20too%20many%20matches%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20the%20other%20commentators%20have%20said%20otherwise.%20But%20if%20you%20come%20and%20open%20and%20then%20have%20a%20strike%20of%20118%20when%20you%20get%20out%20in%20the%2014th%20or%20the%2015th%20over%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20if%20you%20want%20applause%20for%20that%2C%20that's%20a%20little%20bit%20different.%20That's%20different.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20these%20guys%20talk%20about%2C%20'oh%20we%20don't%20care%20about%20outside%20noise'.%20Accha%3F%20Then%20why%20are%20you%20replying%20to%20any%20outside%20noise%20or%20whatever%20it%20is.%20We%20all%20played%20a%20bit%20of%20cricket%2C%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20cricket.%20We%20don't%20have%20agendas.%20We%20speak%20about%20what%20we%20see.%20We%20don't%20necessarily%20have%20any%20likes%20and%20dislikes.%20Even%20if%20we%20have%20likes%20and%20dislikes%2C%20we%20actually%20speak%20on%20what%20is%20happening%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Had%20Virat%20Kohli%20Said%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%20didn't%20mince%20his%20words%20as%20he%20slammed%20those%20criticising%20his%20strike-rate%20after%20scoring%2044-ball%2070%20in%20the%20match%20against%20the%20Gujarat%20Titans%20for%20the%20first%20time%20this%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20really%2C%20I%20think%20all%20the%20people%20who%20talk%20about%20strike%20rates%20and%20me%20not%20playing%20spin%20well%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20love%20talking%20about%20this%20stuff.%20But%2C%20for%20me%2C%20it's%20about%20winning%20the%20game%20for%20the%20team.%20And%20there%20is%20a%20reason%20you%20have%20done%20this%20for%2015%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Kohli%20said%20after%20his%20match-winning%20knock%20against%20Gujarat%20in%20the%20presentation%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20done%20this%2C%20day%20in%20and%20day%20out.%20You%20have%20won%20games%20for%20your%20team.%20And%20I%20am%20not%20quite%20sure%20if%20you%20have%20not%20been%20in%20that%20situation%20yourself%2C%20to%20sit%20and%20speak%20about%20the%20game%20from%20a%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20it's%20the%20same%20thing.%20For%20me%2C%20it's%20about%20doing%20the%20job%20for%20the%20team.%20People%20can%20sit%20and%20talk%20about%20their%20own%20ideas%20and%20assumptions%20of%20the%20game.%20But%20those%20who%20have%20done%20it%2C%20day%20in%20and%20day%20out%2C%20they%20know%20what%20they%20are%20doing.%20It's%20kind%20of%20muscle%20memory%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714883820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg