et%20Singh%2C%2028%2C%20all%20Indian%20nationals%20residing%20in%20Edmonton%20have%20been%20charged%20on%20Friday%20with%20first-degree%20murder%20and%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20important%20because%20Canada%20is%20a%20rule-of-law%20country%20with%20a%20strong%20and%20independent%20justice%20system%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20fundamental%20commitment%20to%20protecting%20all%20its%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20Trudeau%20said%20about%20the%20arrests%20on%20Saturday%20at%20a%20Toronto%20gala%20celebrating%20Sikh%20heritage%20and%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20RCMP%20stated%2C%20the%20investigation%20remains%20ongoing%2C%20as%20does%20a%20separate%20and%20distinct%20investigation%20not%20limited%20to%20the%20involvement%20of%20the%20three%20people%20arrested%20yesterday%2C%26quot%3B%20Canadian%20Broadcasting%20Corporation%20(CBC)%20quoted%20Trudeau%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20many%20in%20Canada's%20Sikh%20community%20are%20feeling%20unsafe%20following%20Nijjar's%20killing%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BEvery%20Canadian%20has%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20live%20safely%20and%20free%20from%20discrimination%20and%20threats%20of%20violence%20in%20Canada.%26quot%3B%20The%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20came%20under%20severe%20strain%20following%20Trudeau's%20allegations%20in%20September%20last%20year%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bpotential%26quot%3B%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20agents%20in%20the%20killing%20of%2045-year-old%20Nijjar%2C%20a%20Khalistan%20separatist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20dismissed%20Trudeau's%20charges%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmotivated.%26quot%3B%20The%20presence%20of%20Sikh%20separatist%20groups%20in%20Canada%20has%20long%20frustrated%20India%2C%20which%20had%20designated%20Nijjar%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrorist.%26quot%3B%20After%20three%20Indian%20nationals%20were%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20murder%2C%20Police%20in%20Canada%20said%20they%20had%20worked%20with%20US%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%2C%20without%20giving%20additional%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20suggested%20more%20arrests%20might%20be%20coming.%20Royal%20Canadian%20Mounted%20Police%20(RCMP)%20Assistant%20Commissioner%20David%20Teboul%2C%20the%20force's%20commander%20for%20the%20Pacific%20region%2C%20said%20Friday%20that%20he%20wouldn't%20comment%20on%20the%20alleged%20links%20between%20the%20three%20men%20arrested%20and%20Indian%20officials%20but%20noted%20the%20force%20is%20%26quot%3Binvestigating%20connections%20to%20the%20government%20of%20India.%26quot%3B%20Meanwhile%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20on%20Saturday%20said%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20poll-bound%20Canada%20over%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar%20is%20mostly%20due%20to%20their%20internal%20politics%20and%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20a%20section%20of%20pro-Khalistan%20people%20are%20using%20Canada's%20democracy%2C%20creating%20a%20lobby%20and%20have%20become%20a%20vote%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20party%20in%20Canada%20has%20no%20majority%20in%20Parliament%20and%20some%20parties%20depend%20on%20pro-Khalistan%20leaders%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20convinced%20them%20several%20times%20not%20to%20give%20visa%2C%20legitimacy%20or%20political%20space%20to%20such%20people%20which%20is%20causing%20problems%20for%20them%20(Canada)%2C%20for%20us%20and%20also%20for%20our%20relationship%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Canadian%20government%20has%20not%20done%20anything%2C%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20India%20sought%20the%20extradition%20of%2025%20people%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20are%20pro-Khalistan%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20pay%20any%20heed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCanada%20did%20not%20give%20any%20proof.%20They%20do%20not%20share%20any%20evidence%20with%20us%20in%20certain%20cases%2