tranj-move-in-raebareli-masterstroke-or-blunder-5587013%5C%22%3EOpinion%20%7C%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20'%3Ci%3EShatranj%3C%2Fi%3E'%20Move%20In%20Raebareli%20-%20Masterstroke%20Or%20Blunder%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECredit%20must%20be%20given%20to%20Kishori%20Lal%20Sharma%2C%20a%20local%20candidate%20who%20is%20well-acquainted%20with%20the%20constituency%20and%20enjoys%20popularity%20as%20a%20Brahmin%2C%20aligning%20with%20the%20party's%20strategy%20to%20regain%20traditional%20support%20from%20upper%20castes%2C%20tribals%2C%20Dalits%2C%20and%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitically%2C%20this%20move%20has%20provided%20ammunition%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20to%20target%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20and%20the%20Congress.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20already%20criticised%20this%20move%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20using%20it%20as%20fodder%20for%20attacks%20during%20election%20rallies.%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20also%20questioned%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20numerous%20launches%2C%20highlighting%20his%20shifts%20from%20Amethi%20to%20Wayanad%2C%20and%20now%20Raebareli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%20Numbers%20Indicated%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20has%20represented%20the%20Amethi%20seat%20since%202004%2C%20losing%20it%20only%20in%202019%20to%20Smriti%20Irani.%20He%20currently%20represents%20Kerala's%20Wayanad%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NDTV%20Data%20Centre%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20won%20Amethi%2015%20out%20of%2018%20times%20and%20Raebareli%2017%20out%20of%2020%20times.%20The%20latter%2C%20traditionally%20held%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20is%20considered%20the%20pocket%20borough%20of%20the%20Gandhi-Nehru%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20Party's%20organisation%20in%20Raebareli%20is%20stronger%20compared%20to%20Amethi.%20The%20BJP's%20Dinesh%20Pratap%20Singh%20is%20not%20seen%20as%20a%20major%20contender%20against%20Rahul%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20electoral%20performance%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20a%2046%25%20vote%20share%20in%20Amethi%20in%202014%2C%20which%20dropped%20to%2043%25%20in%202019.%20In%20Raebareli%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20consistently%20secured%20a%2055-56%25%20vote%20share%20in%20recent%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famethi-rae-bareli-elections-2024-rae-bareli-is-congresss-safe-seat-except-it-handed-defeat-to-a-pm-once-5578108%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Raebareli%20Is%20Congress's%20Safe%20Seat%2C%20Except%20It%20Handed%20Defeat%20To%20A%20PM%20Once%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20SP%20and%20its%20allies%20won%20four%20out%20of%20five%20seats%2C%20while%20in%20Amethi%2C%20the%20BJP%20secured%20three%20and%20the%20SP%20two%20seats.%20Given%20the%20Congress's%20alliance%20with%20the%20SP%20now%2C%20Raebareli%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20safer%20bet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Rahul%20had%20contested%20from%20Amethi%20and%20lost%20again%2C%20it%20would%20have%20weakened%20his%20position%20within%20the%20Congress%20Party.%20This%20is%20likely%20why%20Rahul%20opted%20for%20a%20safer%20seat%2C%20making%20a%20practical%20rather%20than%20an%20emotional%20decision.%20Additionally%2C%20he%20has%20been%20out%20of%20touch%20with%20the%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Priyanka%20could%20have%20contested%20from%20Amethi%20to%20challenge%20Smriti%2C%20which%20could%20have%20kept%20the%20party%20cadre%20motivated%20and%20sent%20a%20strong%20message%20across%20the%20state%20and%20the%20Hindi%20heartland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Move%20That%20Backfired%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20may%20be%20hoping%20to%20convey%20a%20message%20that%20any%20party%20cadre%20or%20worker%20can%20secure%20a%20party%20ticket%2C%20aiming%20to%20deflect%20allegations%20of%20dynasty%20politics.%20Some%20news%20reports%20suggest%20that%20Rahul%20wishes%20to%20retain%20the%20Wayanad%20seat%20due%20to%20the%20warm%20reception%20from%20voters%20and%20his%20successful%20election%20there%20in%202019.%20If%20he%20were%20to%20win%2C%20he%20could%20vacate%20the%20seat%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20by-poll%20battle%20for%20Priyanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20won%20SP%20stronghold%20seats%20like%20Rampur%20and%20Azamgarh%20in%20by-polls%2C%20a%20fact%20Congress%20needs%20to%20consider%20carefully.%20If%20Priyanka%20is%20eventually%20pitched%20to%20represent%20the%20constituency%2C%20why%20not%20field%20her%20in%20this%20election%20itself%20instead%20of%20waiting%20for%20a%20by-poll%3F%20Had%20she%C2%A0been%20fielded%20from%20Raebareli%2C%20the%20BJP%20might%20not%20have%20had%20the%20ammunition%20to%20attack%20Rahul%20with%20charges%20like%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ebhago%20mat%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20by%20Modi%20and%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ere-launch%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20by%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20strategic%20move%20has%20its%20pros%20and%20cons.%20Whether%20this%20decision%20turns%20out%20to%20be%20a%20masterstroke%20or%20a%20misstep%20will%20only%20be%20revealed%20after%20the%20poll%20results%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714879140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fmjbcqrog_rahul-gandhi_625x300_03_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-election-why-did-rahul-choose-raebareli-over-amethi-5591461%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Politically%2C%20the%20Congres's%20move%20has%20provided%20ammunition%20to%20the%20BJP%20to%20target%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20and%20the%20Congress.%22%2