%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fradicalised-16-year-old-shot-dead-by-australian-police-after-stabbing%2Famp_articleshow%2F109850944.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWas%20Really%20Ill%2C%20Felt%20I%20Won't%20Be%20Able%20to%20Play%26quot%3B%3A%20Mohammed%20Siraj%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20Mohammed%20Siraj%2C%20it%20was%20mind%20over%20matter%20as%20he%20pushed%20his%20physically%20indisposed%20self%20to%20the%20limits%20to%20earn%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'%20award%20in%20RCB's%20four%20wicket%20victory%20over%20Gujarat%20Titans%20in%20an%20IPL%20match%20here%20on%20Saturday.%20Siraj%20removed%20openers%20Wriddhiman%20Saha%20and%20opposition%20skipper%20Shubman%20Gill%20in%20his%20first%20spell%20to%20push%20GT%20on%20the%20backfoot%20and%20that%20went%20a%20long%20way%20in%20restricting%20the%20visitors%20to%20a%20modest%20147.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20really%20ill%20for%20the%20last%20few%20days.%20Thought%20I%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20play%20today%20but%20I%20really%20wanted%20to%20play%20so%20it%20was%20great%20that%20I%20was%20able%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Siraj%20said%20after%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20wasn't%20well%2C%20in%20his%20mind%2C%20he%20had%20envisaged%20how%20he%20would%20bowl%20that%20perfectly%20pitched%20up%20delivery%20which%20will%20grow%20big%20on%20the%20batter%20and%20there%20couldn't%20have%20been%20a%20better%20execution%20against%20Wriddhiman%2C%20who%20didn't%20have%20the%20technique%20to%20handle%20such%20a%20ball.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20woke%20up%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20play%20and%20that%20I%20should%20take%20rest.%20When%20I%20woke%20up%2C%20I%20manifested%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20and%20that's%20exactly%20what%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20Siraj%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERCB%20skipper%20Faf%20du%20Plessis%20seemed%20happy%20to%20have%20won%20three%20back-to-back%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeen%20really%20good%20last%20couple%20of%20games%2C%20the%20way%20we've%20played%20with%20bat%20and%20ball.%20We%20have%20been%20unbelievable%20on%20the%20field.%20Something%20around%20180-90%20would%20have%20been%20a%20good%20score%2C%26quot%3B%20Du%20Plessis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDu%20Plessis's%2063%20off%2024%20balls%20with%2010%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes%20went%20a%20long%20way%20in%20ensuring%20that%20RCB%20climbed%20to%20the%20seventh%20spot%20by%20finishing%20the%20game%20in%20little%20under%2014%20overs.%20%26quot%3BProbably%20not%20the%20best%20but%20you're%20trying%20to%20be%20positive%2C%20get%20your%20net%20run-rate%20up.%20It%20makes%20sense%20from%20that%20point%20of%20view%20but%20it%20gets%20to%20the%20point%20when%20you%20need%20to%20show%20a%20bit%20of%20calmness%20and%20composure%20-%20probably%20around%20four%20down%2C%20so%20some%20lessons%20to%20be%20learned%20from%20that.%26quot%3B%20Gujarat%20Titans%20skipper%20Shubman%20Gill%20said%20that%20his%20team%20now%20only%20can%20focus%20on%20winning%20their%20remaining%20games%20and%20control%20the%20controllables%20%26quot%3BIt%20depends%20on%20the%20wicket.%20First%20couple%20of%20overs%20you%20get%20a%20good%20idea%20and%20play%20according%20to%20that.%20I%20think%20170-80%20on%20this%20wicket%20would%20have%20been%20a%20good%20total.%20How%20we%20batted%20in%20the%20powerplay%2C%20and%20how%20they%20bowled%2C%20decided%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20have%20had%20one%20extra%20bowler%20but%20losing%20three%20wickets%20in%20the%20powerplay%20(changed%20planning).%20Very%20important%20to%20start%20from%20zero%20in%20our%20next%20match%20and%20move%20on%20from%20this%20game.%20Learn%20from%20mistakes%20and%20not%20repeat%20them.%20All%20about%20winning%20from%20here%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20synd