former%20Tesla%20employee%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D4793dfcde81f32cc1cd9fb346cd205ad9d24e5255d2e1149dec30c8bee6b158b%26postID%3D6635a8afa7714381cef5faf7%26postSlug%3Dtesla-fsd-full-self-driving-san-francisco-sunset-district-testing-2024-5%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.theinformation.com%252Farticles%252Fhow-tesla-used-a-san-francisco-neighborhood-to-improve-its-driverless-technology%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Information%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E's%20major%20promises%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-robotaxi-not-enough-model-2-needed-wedbush-analysts-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eautonomous%20taxis%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20hinges%20on%20Tesla's%20ability%20to%20improve%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-reason-tesla-giving-full-self-driving-free-trial-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFull%20Self-Driving%20(FSD)%3C%2Fa%3E%20technology%2C%20a%20driver-assistance%20feature%20that%20can%20change%20lanes%2C%20enter%20and%20exit%20highway%20ramps%2C%20recognize%20traffic%20lights%20and%20signs%2C%20and%20self-park%20under%20driver%20supervision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFSD%20differs%20from%20the%20company's%20Autopilot%20feature%2C%20which%20is%20essentially%20an%20advanced%20cruise%20control%20mode%20that%20can%20also%20auto-steer%20within%20clearly%20marked%20lanes%2C%20according%20to%20Tesla's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EV%20maker%20has%20encountered%20various%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-full-self-driving-software-fsd-bugs-video-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etechnical%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-fsd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elegal%20issues%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20FSD%20system%20as%20it%20races%20to%20meet%20Musk's%20ever-shifting%20deadlines%20%E2%80%94%20the%20CEO%20announced%20on%20X%20last%20month%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20he%20plans%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-to-reveal-robotaxi-this-year-elon-musk-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunveil%20Tesla's%20robotaxi%20in%20August%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20employee%20told%20The%20Information%20that%20one%20such%20technical%20problem%20Tesla%20recently%20encountered%20was%20driving%20its%20vehicles%20in%20San%20Francisco's%20Sunset%20District%2C%20a%20neighborhood%20bordered%20by%20Golden%20Gate%20Park%20to%20the%20north%20and%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%20to%20the%20west.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20The%20Information%20noted%20in%20its%20report%2C%20some%20of%20Sunset's%20roads%20have%20dedicated%20lanes%20for%20public%20transportation%20%E2%80%94%20although%20that's%20not%20unique%20to%20the%20neighborhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20city's%20Municipal%20Railway%20(MUNI)%20light%20rail%20bisecting%20Judah%20Street%20in%20the%20Sunset%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224608%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22San%20Francisco%20Sunset%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6636b5d310dfcda40966d1aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESan%20Francisco%20Municipal%20Railway's%20light%20rail%20approaches%20a%20stop%20in%20the%20Sunset%20District.%3Cp%3ELloyd%20Lee%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20fixture%20of%20Sunset's%20streets%20also%20comes%20with%20turn%20restrictions.%20Drivers%20are%20forbidden%20in%20some%20intersections%20from%20making%20left%20turns%2C%20U-turns%2C%20and%20rights%20on%20red.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20major%20road%20that%20borders%20the%20north%20of%20Sunset%2C%20Lincoln%20Way%2C%20is%20divided%20by%20barriers%20or%20narrow%20medians.%20Drivers%20have%20intermittent%20opportunities%20on%20the%20road%20to%20make%20left%20turns%20%E2%80%94%20some%20protected%20and%20others%20unprotected%20%E2%80%94%20while%20other%20parts%20of%20Lincoln%20Way%20restrict%20drivers%20from%20making%20any%20left%20turns%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eif%20other%20aspects%20of%20Sunset's%20grid%20trip%20up%20Tesla's%20FSD%20more%20than%20other%20San%20Francisco%20neighborhoods.%20A%20Tesla%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224608%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20in%20San%20Francisco.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66369cc4ec0c696569011c2f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Tesla%20makes%20an%20unprotected%20left%20turn%20on%20Lincoln%20Way%2C%20a%20major%20road%20in%20San%20Francisco's%20Sunset%20District.%3Cp%3ELloyd%20Lee%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETesla's%20team%2C%20however%2C%20found%20that%20drivers%20in%20the%20Sunset%20often%20had%20to%20intervene%20with%20the%20vehicle's%20FSD%20by%20taking%20control%20of%20the%20wheel%2C%20a%20former%20Tesla%20employee%20told%20The%20Information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20the%20problem%2C%20Tesla%20deployed%20dozens%20of%20test%20drivers%20and%20had%20engineers%20focus%20on%20providing%20software%20updates%20that%20could%20improve%20the%20FSD%20experience%20in%20the%20neighborhood%2C%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20didn't%20state%20whether%20those%20efforts%20vastly%20improved%20the%20feature%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ETesla%20still%20dominates%20in%20San%20Francisco%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESan%20Francisco%20as%20a%20whole%20%E2%80%94%20with%20its%20dense%20population%2C%20restricted%20and%20one-way%20streets%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20vast%20artery%20of%20public%20transportation%20%E2%80%94%20can%20be%20a%20tricky%20city%20for%20novice%20drivers%20to%20navigate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20street%20that%20was%20once%20notoriously%20difficult%20for%20Tesla's%20FSD%20to%20work%20in%20was%20Lombard%20Street%2C%20a%20steep%20and%20windy%20road%20northwest%20of%20San%20Francisco.%20In%202021%2C%20one%20YouTuber%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIl4asorQEhU%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%20Raj%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20recorded%20himself%20constantly%20intervening%20with%20the%20system%20as%20the%20car%20veered%20toward%20the%20road's%20edges.%20The%20video%20also%20showed%20that%20the%20FSD%20system%20would%2C%20at%20one%20point%2C%20hallucinate%20objects%20around%20the%20street%2C%20quickly%20blinking%20images%20of%20a%20car%20or%20human%20figure%20on%20the%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22911%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lombard%20Street%20in%20San%20Francisco%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6636abea0dfb1341e902aa4c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESan%20Francisco's%20famously%20winding%20Lombard%20Street%3Cp%3ETayfun%20Coskun%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Bernal%2C%20a%20former%20Tesla%20employee%20who%20worked%20with%20the%20Autopilot%20team%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Ftechnology%2F2023%2F03%2F19%2Felon-musk-tesla-driving%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023%20that%20Tesla%20engineers%20coded%20invisible%20barriers%20into%20FSD%20specifically%20for%20Lombard%20Street%20instead%20of%20making%20broader%20changes%20to%20the%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20city%20is%20teeming%20with%20Teslas.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spglobal.com%2Fmobility%2Fen%2Fresearch-analysis%2Ffirstever-major-us-metro-area-hits-50-electrified-vehicle-regi.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%