eed%20constant%20direction.%20They'll%20tackle%20some%20tasks%2C%20presumably%20simpler%20ones%2C%20instantly%2C%20Altman%20said.%20They'll%20make%20a%20first%20pass%20at%20more%20complex%20tasks%2C%20and%20come%20back%20to%20the%20user%20if%20they%20have%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bottom%20line%20is%20that%20Altman%20wants%20AI%20to%20function%20as%20more%20than%20just%20a%20chatbot.%20It%20should%20help%20people%20accomplish%20things%20in%20the%20real%20world%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20would%20be%20a%20massive%20step%20up%20from%20what%20OpenAI%20offers%20right%20now.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20reportedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereferred%20to%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20%26quot%3Bincredibly%20dumb%26quot%3B%20even%20though%20workers%20are%20already%20using%20it%20to%20accelerate%20their%20workflows%2C%20develop%20code%2C%20write%20emails%2C%20and%20more.%20So%2C%20there's%20no%20telling%20how%20much%20more%20productive%20we'll%20get%20once%20Altman's%20magical%20model%20colleague%20hits%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20didn't%20specify%20when%20this%20tool%20will%20be%20available%20and%20how%20advanced%20AI%20must%20be%20to%20support%20it.%20The%20company's%20other%20offerings%2C%20like%20the%20video%20generator%2C%20Sora%2C%20and%20image%20generator%2C%20DALL-E%2C%20still%20require%20considerable%20guidance%20to%20complete%20tasks.%20They%20also%20aren't%20designed%20to%20perceive%20information%20from%20the%20environment%20and%20use%20it%20to%20achieve%20specific%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20OpenAI's%20forthcoming%20language%20model%2C%20GPT-5%2C%20might%20be%20a%20step%20in%20that%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20source%20who's%20seen%20it%20previously%20told%20BI%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-launch-better-gpt-5-chatbot-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C