%20staying%20our%20course%2C%20has%20built%20trust%20in%20our%20social%20investors.%E2%80%9D%20And%20what%E2%80%99s%20amazing%20is%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317213%2Fhow-to-apply-isb-accelerator-programme-for-social-impact-startups%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethese%20investors%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20witness%20impact%20at%20scale.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CImagine!%20A%20person%20living%20in%20Mumbai%20can%20invest%20in%20someone%20who%20is%20in%20Matheran.%20What%E2%80%99s%20more%2C%20is%20that%20the%20RBI%20gives%20the%20person%20who%20is%20borrowing%20money%20the%20same%20status%20as%20he%20would%20get%20if%20he%20were%20borrowing%20from%20a%20bank.%20He%20will%20get%20a%20credit%20score%20in%20all%20the%20four%20credit%20bureaus%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20clarifies%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20how%20the%20Matheran%20project%20strikes%20a%20chord%20in%20him%2C%20Ram%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20liberating%20to%20know%20that%20a%20practice%20(hand-pulled%20rickshaws)%20that%20has%20been%20in%20existence%20since%20the%20British%20era%20will%20be%20put%20to%20an%20end.%E2%80%9D%20He%20sees%20this%20as%20a%20classic%20textbook%20example%20of%20blending%20many%20social%20factors%20%E2%80%94%20engaging%20communities%2C%20protecting%20the%20environment%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318643%2Fengineer-helps-mir-nomadic-community-gujarat-sell-traditional-beadwork-tokar-designs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreating%20dignified%20livelihoods%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20into%20one.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20road%20Rang%20De%20is%20traversing%2C%20Ram%20says%20it%20is%20a%20long%20one.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20impact%20a%20million%20social%20investors%20and%20households%20that%20the%20investment%20is%20helping.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Shinde%20who%20now%20watches%20with%20happiness%20as%20his%20friend%20drives%20an%20e-rickshaw%2C%20feels%20proud.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20happy%20I%20could%20do%20my%20bit%20for%20the%20locals%20of%20Matheran%2C%20who%20take%20great%20pride%20in%20their%20work.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInvest%20in%20an%20e-rickshaw%20and%20help%20hand%20rickshaw%20pullers%20today!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frangde.in%2Ffund%2Fmatheranerickshawfund%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInvest%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EUnable%20to%20view%20the%20above%20button%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frangde.in%2Ffund%2Fmatheranerickshawfund%5C%22%3EClick%20here%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714627337000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmatheran-_11zon-1714626048.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D348640%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20Sunil%20Shinde%2C%20a%20retired%20teacher%2C%20petitioned%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20allow%20e-rickshaws%20in%20Matheran%2C%20he%20was%20just%20trying%20to%20help%20his%20friends%20who%20were%20hand-rickshaw-pullers.%20Today%2C%20his%20initiative%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20movement%20made%20possible%20by%20%26quot%3BRang%20De'%2C%20a%20social%20peer-to-peer%20lending%20platform.%20Here's%20how%20you%20can%20help.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348640%2Fhand-rickshaw-pullers-e-rickshaws-in-matheran-maharashtra-need-investment-campaign-rang-de-platform%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pottery%2C%20Pool%20%26amp%3B%20Paddy%20Fields%3A%20We%20Moved%20From%20Mumbai%20to%20Goa%20To%20Build%20Our%20Dream%20Homestay%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEight-year-old%20Devaki%20Nair%20waits%20in%20anticipation%20for%20the%20school%20bell%20to%20ring%20so%20she%20can%20rush%20home.%20Today%2C%20like%20most%20days%2C%20she%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20relay%20to%20her%20mother%20Kavita%20%E2%80%94%20how%20her%20day%20went%2C%20the%20new%20topics%20she%20learnt%20at%20school%2C%20and%20the%20names%20of%20the%20friends%20she%20made.%20Luckily%20for%20her%2C%20the%20school%20is%20a%20short%20walk%20from%20the%20Parijaat%20Goa%20Homestay%2C%20which%20is%20also%20where%20Devaki%20lives%20with%20her%20parents%20Kavita%20and%20Manoj%20Nair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20a%20sprawling%20paradise%20of%20a%20place%2C%20the%20little%20girl%20does%20not%20need%20to%20wander%20much%20to%20find%20her%20mother.%20She%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20in%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298110%2Fharyana-engineer-revives-traditional-pottery-earns-lakhs-by-selling-clay-utensils%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epottery%20studio%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20sits%20beside%20the%20towering%20tamarind%20tree.%20Right%20enough%2C%20Kavita%20is%20moulding%20wet%20clay%20into%20utensils%20and%20delicate%20urns%20that%20she%20neatly%20arranges%20along%20the%20studio%E2%80%99s%20many%20shelves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevaki%20watches%20on%20intently%2C%20admiring%20the%20alchemy%20of%20clay%20being%20given%20life%20through%20these%20items.%20Then%2C%20once%20she%20is%20sure%20she%20isn%E2%80%99t%20interrupting%20the%20process%2C%20she%20begins%20to%20chat.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20my%20favourite%20part%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAnother%20favourite%20part%20of%20my%20day%20is%20playing%20with%20my%20friend%20Deep.%E2%80%9D%20As%20Kavita%20explains%2C%20Deep%20is%20the%20caretaker%E2%80%99s%20son%20who%20has%20grown%20up%20alongside%20Devaki%20on%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3